label("(G) $\begin{pmatrix} 40 \\ 16 \end{pmatrix}$", 2*x);
label("(H) $\begin{pmatrix} 4 \\ 10 \end{pmatrix}$", 3*x);
[/asy]

Enter the letters of the correct options, separated by commas. The final Answer is \text{B, E, G}
 ### Proof
